/android/app/release

# Firebase client configs — kept out of version control to satisfy secret
# scanning. These contain Firebase client API keys which are public-by-design
# per Firebase docs (they ship in the published APK/IPA), but GitHub flags
# them regardless. Prod release builds inject these from GitHub Secrets
# GOOGLE_SERVICES_JSON and GOOGLE_SERVICE_INFO_PLIST (see mobile.yml).
# For local prod-flavor builds, download from Firebase Console into:
#   android/app/src/prod/google-services.json
#   ios/Runner/GoogleService-Info.plist
android/app/src/prod/google-services.json
ios/Runner/GoogleService-Info.plist
